---
title: North Indian Inspired Beef and Spinach Curry with Basmati Rice
description: This delicious North Indian Inspired Beef and Spinach Curry has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R25_W38_UK_L14549-5_Main__1low-1803a779.jpg
